{"tid":874971,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】一齊嚟睇風景畫","createTime":"2018-10-24T14:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T15:43:55.000Z","uid":140965,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7594cd0f2037334525dfb9b08794fce62bdd29","tid":874971,"uid":140965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"喺呢個個個碌ig睇女睇相睇漫畫嘅年代<br />\n已經冇乜人會睇風景畫<br />\n<br />\n等我今晚分享幾幅19世紀美國畫家嘅風景畫啦<br />\n有時啲風景喺畫家筆下仲靚過實景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畫家: Frederic Edwin Church<br />\n<br />\nTwilight in the Wilderness<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/98/Twilight_in_the_Wilderness_by_Frederic_Edwin_Church_%283%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F9%2F98%2FTwilight_in_the_Wilderness_by_Frederic_Edwin_Church_%25283%2529.jpg&h=31dcd6c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCotopaxi<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/60/Cotopaxi_church.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F6%2F60%2FCotopaxi_church.jpg&h=70db171e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJerusalem from the Mount of Olives<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/90/Frederic_Edwin_Church_-_Jerusalem_from_the_Mount_of_Olives_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F9%2F90%2FFrederic_Edwin_Church_-_Jerusalem_from_the_Mount_of_Olives_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg&h=f18e99f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNiagara<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0b/Frederic_church_-_niagara_falls.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F0b%2FFrederic_church_-_niagara_falls.jpg&h=b6caff26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nView of Cotopaxi<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/01/View_of_Cotopaxi_by_Frederic_Edwin_Church_1857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F01%2FView_of_Cotopaxi_by_Frederic_Edwin_Church_1857.jpg&h=3fbe3a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCotopaxi (佢都幾鐘意呢個火山<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bc/Cotopaxi_%281855%29_Frederic_Edwin_Church.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fbc%2FCotopaxi_%25281855%2529_Frederic_Edwin_Church.jpg&h=e46ac0b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Andes of Ecuador<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9d/Frederic_Edwin_Church%2C_The_Andes_of_Ecuador%2C_c._1855%2C_HAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F9%2F9d%2FFrederic_Edwin_Church%252C_The_Andes_of_Ecuador%252C_c._1855%252C_HAA.jpg&h=7aec0043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Wreck<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/33/The_Wreck_Frederic_Edwin_Church.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F33%2FThe_Wreck_Frederic_Edwin_Church.jpg&h=76b54594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Natural Bridge, Virginia<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c3/Frederic_Edwin_Church_-_The_Natural_Bridge%2C_Virginia.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fc%2Fc3%2FFrederic_Edwin_Church_-_The_Natural_Bridge%252C_Virginia.jpg&h=19e8c1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRainy Season in the Tropics<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Frederic_Edwin_Church_-_Rainy_Season_in_the_Tropics_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg/1280px-Frederic_Edwin_Church_-_Rainy_Season_in_the_Tropics_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F8f%2FFrederic_Edwin_Church_-_Rainy_Season_in_the_Tropics_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg%2F1280px-Frederic_Edwin_Church_-_Rainy_Season_in_the_Tropics_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg&h=8e1d9bda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d1b9ef9d5922ea3c999a2a52c0c553a094c369d","tid":874971,"uid":214233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"明明係影相黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你厄我唔到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0037aa0879496c5793c73ca2c8eb474e9c76e7cb","tid":874971,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d1b9ef9d5922ea3c999a2a52c0c553a094c369d","tid":874971,"uid":214233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"明明係影相黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你厄我唔到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"喂喂～<br />\n叫左你唔好打咁多啦"},{"pid":"3c30b533c55fee1280bd9984142999c5f62a90c7","tid":874971,"uid":47529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:05:21.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意風景畫<br />\n記得唔知去邊個博物館睇過一個德國畫家 <br />\n淨係記得同場有the sea by the monk <br />\n都係畫風景 有時會畫啲想像出黎既風景畫 <br />\n例如係有個好靚好大既城堡做前景既畫<br />\n過左五 六年 仍然係我最鍾意既風景畫"},{"pid":"36c26ac86348ff40f7d8c0a5de75e326cbf0882f","tid":874971,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"還可以啦 有一半以上"},{"pid":"9ff1fcd6c770c0440a564b1a6fec1ed36a2e3cb7","tid":874971,"uid":140965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c30b533c55fee1280bd9984142999c5f62a90c7","tid":874971,"uid":47529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-2