2Fcommons%2F4%2F45%2FAlbert_Bierstadt_-_The_Rocky_Mountains%252C_Lander%2527s_Peak.jpg&h=db61d483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRocky Mountains, Lander&rsquo;s Peak<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/98/The_Rocky_Mountains%2C_Lander%27s_Peak_%28Albert_Bierstadt%29%2C_1863_%28oil_on_linen_-_scan%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F9%2F98%2FThe_Rocky_Mountains%252C_Lander%2527s_Peak_%2528Albert_Bierstadt%2529%252C_1863_%2528oil_on_linen_-_scan%2529.jpg&h=ca3fc375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLooking Down the Yosemite Valley, California<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8c/Looking_Down_Yosemite-Valley.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F8c%2FLooking_Down_Yosemite-Valley.jpg&h=0c6811f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Oregon Trail Campfire<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/61/Albert_Bierstadt_-_Oregon_Trail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F6%2F61%2FAlbert_Bierstadt_-_Oregon_Trail.jpg&h=c8c29176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA Rustic Mill Farm<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2c/Albert_Bierstadt_A_Rustic_Mill.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F2%2F2c%2FAlbert_Bierstadt_A_Rustic_Mill.jpg&h=3dc010de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAmong the Sierra Nevada Mountains<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8a/Albert_Bierstadt%2C_Among_the_Sierra_Nevada_Mountains.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F8a%2FAlbert_Bierstadt%252C_Among_the_Sierra_Nevada_Mountains.jpg&h=d9c1328a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEmigrants Crossing the